Joyce TATOR, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. HOUSING AUTHORITY OF THE BIRMINGHAM DISTRICT, Defendant-Appellee. No. 05-13441 D.C. Docket No. 03-00703-CV-P-S.

Non-Argument Calendar.

United States Court of Appeals, Eleventh Circuit. Nov. 28, 2005. Coker Bart Cleveland, Cleveland & Vickers, LLC, Birmingham, AL, for Plaintiff-Appellant. James C. Ayers, Jr., Columbiana, AL, for Defendant-Appellee. Before TJOFLAT, DUBINA and FAY, Circuit Judges. PER CURIAM:

The summary judgment granted in favor of the appellee is affirmed for the reasons set forth in the thorough Memorandum *194Opinion entered by the district court on January 19,2005.

AFFIRMED.
